pid":"7032f7b0361ff47924aff9278acca2bd07403372","tid":1010132,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T02:32:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收皮啦"},{"pid":"c2cbef8e91f8da8271c828412fd539fe22a11ced","tid":1010132,"uid":38203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:41:35.000Z","msg":"不想放大只想放大被放大"},{"pid":"f103dc5f56dc59b2f55e75114aa5e6b4b3d95ecc","tid":1010132,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T03:46:25.000Z","msg":"平心而論佢呢個答法叫做謙厚咗<br />\n唔似以前話自己係天才、叻仔我可以肥乜乜柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ee14a01596c99df34045101ca6f89130e1bb3a","tid":1010132,"uid":178205,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:33:01.000Z","msg":"好多戇鳩會話春風又綠江南岸係錯文法<br />\n<br />\n實際上就係顯示自己無知<br />\n<br />\n古文有使動句式 啫係使江南岸綠了<br />\n<br />\n係合文法嘅<br />\n<br />\n李白嘅詩都有 東風已綠瀛州草<br />\n<br />\n現代白話文 你咪唔啱囉戇鳩仔"}]}